name: adidas Women Amalgo W Running Shoe
description: The two parts higher quality EVA MIDSOLE concept created provides extra cushion, comfort, flexibility and resilience from toe-off through every phase of your stride. It is delivered in dual colours to create an aesthetically pleasing footwear. Half midsole design promotes a great fit and all-day comfort while the soft underfoot feel comes from a springy midsole foam that creates a smooth ride.

name: adidas Women Base X W Running Shoes
description: Elevate your running experience with the Adidas Base X W shoes, designed for both exceptional comfort and performance. The breathable mesh upper ensures optimal ventilation, keeping your feet cool and dry during intense workouts.

name: Adidas Grand Court 2.0 Unisex Casual Sneaker
description: The added forefoot flex plus a Cloudfoam Comfort sockliner in these men's adidas shoes create a luxe feel. The 3-Stripes pick up colours from World Friendship Day. A flagship model for sustaiNot applicablebility, the shoes boast a synthetic leather upper.

description: When you're ready to get serious about running, you're ready for adidas Adi-Shawt Shoes. They feature a breathable mesh upper along with an EVA midsole which provides optimum cushioning where you need it most. The rubber outsole offers ample traction and skid resistance. Embossing along the mid-foot lends it a 3D look.

name: adidas Women Galaxy 6 W Running Shoe
description: It was true then, and it's true now. adidas designs shoes with athletes in mind. These running shoes can be worn anytime, but they're still equipped with some innovative tech. The lightweight mesh upper lets air flow, and the Cloudfoam midsole gives a springy, cushioned feel. A soft sockliner keeps feet feeling supported, no matter how often you put them through a long walk or workout. Made with a series of recycled materials, this upper features at least 50% recycled content. This product represents just one of our solutions to help end plastic waste.

name: adidas Men Vac-Run Running Shoe
description: Wherever your run takes you, your running shoes should give you comfort, protection and support where and when you need it most. We have the right product for you. Running is perhaps the purest, most universal form of fitness. Whether you're competing on the track, aiming for a marathon, a 5k run or a jog in the park, running is open to us all. The Textile Upper Feels Comfy And Breathable, And The Rubber Outsole Gives You Plenty Of Grip For A Confident Stride. An Ortholite sockliner provides additional cushioning.

name: Nike Men Shoes
description: The M ZOOM GP CHALLENGE PRO HC PRM is a high-performance running shoe designed for serious athletes and enthusiasts. Featuring a lightweight and breathable upper, it ensures optimal comfort and support during intense workouts. The shoe incorporates advanced cushioning technology that absorbs impact, providing a responsive feel with every stride. Its durable outsole offers excellent traction on various surfaces, making it suitable for both road and trail running. The sleek design is complemented by vibrant color options, appealing to those who value style as much as performance. Ideal for competitive runners, the M ZOOM GP CHALLENGE PRO HC PRM is engineered to enhance speed and efficiency.
